{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1677-11_044","@resp":"mercure","head":{"value":"[Epistre en Vers à Monsieur le Duc de S. Aignan]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Le Nouveau Mercure Galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#1":{"value":", novembre 1677 (tome IX), p. 44-50","id":"/div/bibl/#1"},"note":{"@resp":"editor","#":{"value":"Il existe une autre édition parisienne, réalisée \"Suivant la Copie imprimée\" par Theodore Girard, dont la pagination diffère.","id":"/div/bibl/note/#"}},"#2":{"value":".","id":"/div/bibl/#2"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"Comme les Charges &amp; les grands Emplois font plutost honte qu’honneur si on ne les soûtient par le merite, heureux qui en est liberalement partagé. Je sçay bien que la Cour est un grand Theatre où il paroist avec beaucoup plus d’éclat qu’ailleurs ; mais il n’y est pas si fort renfermé qu’il ne se répande dans les Provinces, &amp; vous conviendrez de celuy de M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Petit, quand vous aurez leu ce que je vous envoye de sa façon. C’est une Epistre enjoüée qu’il adresse à Monsieur le Duc de S. Aignan, qui a pour luy une estime tres-particuliere. Le stile en est libre, &amp; vous y trouverez un tour aisé qui vous persuadera aisément de ce que j’ay à vous dire à l’avantage de son Autheur.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"À MONSIEUR ","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"LE DUC DE S. AIGNAN.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’est-il point fait cet Armement","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui depuis long temps vous occupe ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Apollon s’en plaint hautement,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi qu’Amour le Dieu charmant ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et le beau Sexe porte jupe,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy, Seigneur, ne parlera-t-on","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En ce Siecle que de Canon,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de prendre d’assaut des Villes,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de punir les Ennemis","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De leurs manieres inciviles","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’oser se frotter à","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Loüis","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/hi[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":",","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le premier Héros de la Terre,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sçavant au noble Art de la Guerre,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout comme celuy qui le fit,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et donc la gloire retentit","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mieux que le bruit de son Tonnerre ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[15]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nostre Parnasse est sans Laurier ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais qui pourroit à ce Guerrier","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En fournir assez pour sa teste ?","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Muses mesmes sont à bout ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elles pensent avoit dit tout,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et leur Chant sur une Conqueste","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vient à grand’ peine de cesser,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que la surprenante nouvelle","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une autre &amp; plus grande &amp; plus belle,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les oblige à recommencer.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin ce Conquerant terrible","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lasse Muses, Chefs &amp; Soldats,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et pare qu’il est Invincible,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il ne se trouve jamais las.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais tandis qu’il tient dans la Plaine","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ses braves Héros en haleine,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Apres bien de tristes helas,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mille Belles disent en larmes,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ah, maudite gloire des Armes,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Maudits Assauts, maudits Combats,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que vous nous causez de tristesse !","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que nous perdons de doux ébats,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que tant de belle Noblesse","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seroit bien mieux entre nos bras !","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais que voulez-vous davantage ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Grand Monarque, vos Ennemis","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne sont-ils pas vaincus, soûmis :","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De tous costez pliant bagage ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Laissez donc Mars avec sa rage,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et rendant à l’Amour hommage,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Daignez nous rendre nos Amis.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous n’y perdrez rien, digne Prince,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Non, Grand Roy, vous n’y perdrez rien,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nos amours dans chaque Province","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Feront naistre des Gens de bien.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce seront des Sujets fidelles","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont se peuplera vostre Cour,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Masles bien faits, belles Femelles,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tous Enfans de Mars &amp; d’Amour.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[28]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’ont-elles pas raison, ces Belles ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je veux vous en prendre à témoin,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous, qui toûjours avec grand soin","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fistes mille choses pour elles.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Amour n’est-il pas plus plaisant","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que la Guerre, dont la furie","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jamais n’agit qu’en détruisant","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le tresor des tresors, la vie ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Oüy, tout compté, tout rabatu,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seigneur, l’amoureuse vertu","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vaut mieux que la vertu guerriere.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cela ne se peut contester,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car enfin donner la lumiere","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est plus noble que de l’oster.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[13]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy qu’il en soit, pour satisfaire","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aux justes plaintes de ces Dieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et pour appaiser la colere","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De mille Dames aux beaux yeux ;","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ces Rimes qui sçavent plaire","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Reprenez l’agreable employ,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et sur vostre charmante Lyre","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont par tout les tons on admire,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chantez","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Loüis","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/hi[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":", nostre Grand Roy,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/hi[2]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ensuite, chantez les tendresses","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De l’Amour le Dieu des douceurs,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ces vingt ou trente Maistresses","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont vous avez gagné les cœurs.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[12]/#"}}]}}]}}}